document_data.name: Quetti
document_data.mainbody: '''Quetti''' was the [[orc]] chieftain of the [[Death Horn]] tribe in [[Many-Arrows]] in [[1484 DR]].
document_data.History: Just after the start of the [[Darkening]], Quetti urged King [[Obould XVII]] to start a war with [[Luruar]].
